Season chicken, if desired, with salt and pepper or Knorr(R) Chicken flavor Bouillon. Heat oil in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and cook chicken, stirring frequently, until chicken is thoroughly cooked, about 5 minutes. Stir in lime juice. Remove and set aside. Prepare Knorr(R) Fiesta Sides(TM) - Yellow Rice in same skillet according to package directions. Stir in chicken, avocado and tomato until well blended. Top, if desired, with shredded Cheddar cheese, chopped red onion, and cilantro.